org.s1.weboperation

Class DispatcherServlet

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.servlet.GenericServlet
      • javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
        • org.s1.weboperation.DispatcherServlet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig

    public class DispatcherServlet
extends javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
    Dispatcher servlet. Dispatches requests between web operations. 
     <!-- Main dispatcher servlet. Serves business logic of application. -->
 <servlet>
  <servlet-name>dispatcher</servlet-name>
  <servlet-class>org.s1.weboperation.DispatcherServlet</servlet-class>
  <load-on-startup>1</load-on-startup>
 </servlet>
 <servlet-mapping>
  <servlet-name>dispatcher</servlet-name>
  <url-pattern>/dispatcher/*</url-pattern>
 </servlet-mapping>
